OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776172268
OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe prime minister has said the UK
OL,8,Fwill not get dragged into the war in
OL,9,FIran, and has refused to support
OL,10,FDonald Trump's blockade of Iran's
OL,11,Fports.
OL,13,FThe US military says it will begin a
OL,14,Fblockade of all Iranian ports and
OL,15,Fcoastal areas on Monday, in a move
OL,16,Fthat has once again caused oil prices
OL,17,Fto jump to more than $100 a barrel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
