PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776172268
OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FSpeaking to BBC Radio 5 Live, Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer said: "What we've been doing
OL,9,Fover the last few weeks ` and this was
OL,10,Fpart of what I was discussing with the
OL,11,FGulf states last week ` is bringing
OL,12,Fcountries together to keep the strait
OL,13,Fopen, not shut.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776172268
OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We're not supporting the blockade and
OL,8,Fall of the marshalling diplomatically,
OL,9,Fpolitically and capability ` we do
OL,10,Fhave mine-sweeping capability, I won't
OL,11,Fgo into operational matters, but we do
OL,12,Fhave that capability ` that's all
OL,13,Ffocused, from our point of view, on
OL,14,Fgetting the strait fully open."
OL,16,FUS Central Command said the blockade
OL,17,Fwould be "enforced impartially against
OL,18,Fvessels of all nations", and is due to
OL,19,Fbegin at 10am EDT, or 3pm UK time on
OL,20,FMonday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
