PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776172268
OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FIt added that it will "not impede"
OL,8,Fships using the Strait to travel to
OL,9,Fother countries that are not Iran.
OL,11,FPresident Trump had initially
OL,12,Fthreatened to blockade "any and all
OL,13,Fships trying to enter, or leave, the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz" in a post on Truth
OL,15,FSocial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776172268
OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FStarmer was keen to stress: "My
OL,8,Fdecision has been very clearly that
OL,9,Fwhatever the pressure ` and there's
OL,10,Fbeen some considerable pressure `
OL,11,Fwe're not getting dragged into the
OL,12,Fwar. The UK is not getting dragged in.
OL,14,F"That's not in our national interest,
OL,15,Fbecause I'm not going to act unless
OL,16,Fthere's a clear, lawful basis and a
OL,17,Fclear thought-through plan."
OL,26,@oD@]OUvD@AOUyD@\O]
