OL,3,CStarmer says UK will 'not support'
OL,4,CTrump's blockade of the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FStarmer said these options included
OL,8,F"mine hunting systems", "anti-drone
OL,9,Fcapabilities", and how UK can "play a
OL,10,Fpart in bringing others together" to
OL,11,Fcreate a lasting solution.
